'''Low Town''' was part of the [[City/Legends|city]] [[Barons Hed]] on [[Sulon/Legends|Sulon]]. 

It was the part of town around [[Barons Knoll]] and comprised of the poorest residences, as well as most businesses, in contrast to the [[High Town]], the richer residences built on the slopes of the hill. Citizens of Low Town were often seen with dirt and grease. The alleys that traversed shops, taverns and [[cantina/Legends|cantinas]] were stinking with [[urine/Legends|urine]] and vomit; [[incense/Legends|incense]] was used to cover the stink, creating a mix of odors.<ref name="RA">''[[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent]]''</ref>

The side street gave way to the [[Rimmer's Alley]] which led towards the hill.<ref name="RA" />

